  "time_ut": 1661137408,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0d86\u0db1\u0dba\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd2 \u0dbd\u0ddc\u0dca\u0d9a \u0db6\u0dd0\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0dd9\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Strict regulations from the World Bank in the import of fertilizers",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sunday Times reported that the World Bank has introduced strict regulations to ensure that the procurement process for importing fertilizers for the high season in Sri Lanka is free from fraud and corruption.",
        "The Sunday Times newspaper said that a senior official of the Ministry of Agriculture said that bids will be invited under the international competitive bidding system to import fertilizers for the high season with those strict regulations.",
        "According to World Bank guidelines, contractors and their sub-contractors must allow the World Bank to inspect records, accounts and other documents related to the procurement process of importing fertilizers and allow auditors appointed by the World Bank to audit the entire process.",
        "The Sunday Times reported that the Ministry of Agriculture has called for bids to import 125,000 metric tons of urea for the upcoming season using the funds under the US$350 million emergency financial facility set aside by the World Bank.",
        "Accordingly, the Sunday Times newspaper said that 110 million US dollars were used from that fund to import fertilizer for the season that starts on September 15 and that the fertilizer stock will be delivered to Sri Lanka in 5 batches.",
        "The contractors will be bidding under the International Competitive Bidding System with National Procurement Guidelines in accordance with the World Bank's strict regulations to ensure a fraud and corruption free process.",
        "If contractors have paid commissions or fees to agents in connection with the bidding process, the contractor must disclose to the employer the name, address, and amount paid of the agent to whom the amount was paid, as per World Bank guidelines."
      ],
